description: Nestled in the heart of West Simi Valley, this charming single-story home is offered by the original owner. With a sense of enduring quality, the residence stands as a testament to thoughtful care and attention.The property's prime location offers unparalleled convenience, close proximity to local schools, renowned restaurants, vibrant shopping centers and easy freeway access. Nature enthusiasts and fitness aficionados will delight in the proximity to the Arroyo Simi Greenway, a scenic and dynamic bike and walking path that weaves through the picturesque landscapes of Simi Valley. The greenway provides an ideal escape, offering a tranquil route for leisurely strolls or invigorating bike rides.With its desirable location, meticulous upkeep, and the array of amenities in its vicinity, this property is unquestionably a 'must-see' for those seeking a home that harmonizes comfort, accessibility, and a sense of community. Discover the essence of West Simi Valley living in this inviting and well-loved home.
